      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a dependable vehicle that\u2019s ready to get you where you need to go? This car is in fair condition and has served its previous owner well, showing some honest character and wear from the miles it has traveled. While it has some cosmetic imperfections and signs of age, it remains a solid, functional choice for anyone seeking reliable transportation at a great value!",
